{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-416-a-frogs-trip","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-401-to-480","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 416: Putovanje žabe","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Red pravougaonika $n$ ima žabu u najlijevo ugaonom pravougaoniku. Skakanjem u nizu žaba ide do najdesnije pravougaonika, a zatim se vraća u najlijevi ugaoni pravougaonik. Na izlaznom putu, skaka jedan, dva ili tri pravougaonika udesno, a na povratnom putu skaka ulevo na sličan način. Ne može da skoči izvan linija pravougaonika. Ponavlja ciklični put $m$ puta.</p>\n<p>Neka je $F(m, n)$ broj puteva koje žaba može preći tako da barem jedan pravougaonik ne bude poseta.</p>\n<p>Na primer, $F(1, 3) = 4$, $F(1, 4) = 15$, $F(1, 5) = 46$, $F(2, 3) = 16$ i $F(2, 100)\\bmod {10}^9 = 429\\,619\\,151$.</p>\n<p>Pronađi poslednje 9 cifara za $F(10, {10}^{12})$.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f50e1000cf542c510020","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302085,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-401-to-480/problem-416-a-frogs-trip"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function frogsTrip() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nfrogsTrip();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>frogsTrip()</code> treba da vrati <code>898082747</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(frogsTrip(), 898082747);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-401-to-480","dashedName":"problem-416-a-frogs-trip","certification":"project-euler","disable